data.description: Spacious, well-kept home with lots of character and charm. Fresh paint, 2 large living areas, one with a small office nook, nice-sized eat-in kitchen, laundry room with extra storage space, large room sizes, one has a walk-in closet. Big back yard with a storage shed. Conveniently located near shopping, highways, naval bases, hospitals, restaurants, and centrally situated amid all 7 cities of the Hampton Roads area!
